6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Uizard and Visme share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Ai Generation. Where Uizard pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Responsive, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Visme uniquely offers Animations, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Uizard holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Visme scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Uizard and Visme offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Uizard's free tier and Visme's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
