a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Uizard is best suited for product managers, non designers, rapid prototyping, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Visme, meanwhile, shines for marketers, educators, business professionals, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2018, Uizard describes itself as \"AI-powered UI design tool that turns ideas into interactive prototypes.\" Visme, established in 2013, positions itself as \"Design platform for creating presentations, infographics, and visual content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Uizard** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Visme is a poor choice — far from it. Visme excels in its own right, particularly for marketers and educators.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value generate ui from text descriptions, go with Uizard. If excellent for data visualization matters more to you, Visme is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
